al/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時食爭鮮喺夜晚九點幾嘅時候迴轉帶上面嗰啲三文魚壽司（兩件嗰隻）唔知點解會特別肥，但係叫師傅直接整出嚟嗰啲又會冇咁肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b204b5d3d9bc520737f5898044385fdf1a484a","tid":241881,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐到佢臨收工<br />\n其他食客走哂得返你1個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到嗰陣條迴轉帶上面嗰啲都係係尾水啦，碟碟都係熟悉的面孔都唔知轉咗幾多個圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42689ae25ac07a1615a004d4e325c909bebb7fb","tid":241881,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"用時間停止器<br />\n到時何止食壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b75dc11f0a792feb3a5c829042c311e2a3f5ed","tid":241881,"uid":101986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T16:26:05.000Z","msg":"坐係迴轉帶上面"}]}